Author: toripaitan
Text: being at work has been a living nightmare because I work in an office with catered lunch and a fuck ton of snacks and there’s always some event with food and it makes me feel so out of control because I eat and can’t stop and I tell myself I’ll stop and never do it again but it keeps happening and I literally feel so sick and distressed like I’m trapped in a body that isn’t the body I’m supposed to have
